          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="column">
	  <h2>News</h2><img src="{{ asset('bundles/boldhome/images/img2.png') }}" alt="News" title="" />
          <p>Redeploying to <a href="http://evemaps.dotlan.net/map/Catch/CZK-ZQ">CZK-ZQ</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="column">
          <h2>Have a Question?</h2><img src="{{ asset('bundles/boldhome/images/img3.png') }}" alt="" title="" />
          <p>Join us in our public recruitment channel "BOLD recruitment" if you have any questions about BO-LD.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

{% endblock %}
